te. We demonstrate\nthat this nonlinear filtering can be enhanced by pulse-driving asynchronously,\nin order to preserve the coherence of the comb. Taken together, our work\nestablishes resonant supercontinuum as a promising route to broadband and\ncoherent spectra.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Aug 2019 18:19:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Sep 2019 16:12:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 23 Mar 2020 11:52:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-24"}
