etic data and a real world child welfare dataset to\ndemonstrate how the proposed method improves upon standard practice.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Aug 2019 20:47:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Nov 2019 15:15:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 10 Jan 2020 14:08:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-13"}
