 and validate their data-driven methods. Finally, we evaluate several\nstate-of-the-art approaches on our DIOR dataset to establish a baseline for\nfuture research.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 31 Aug 2019 05:36:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 22 Sep 2019 02:13:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-06"}
